12:T48e,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"VideoObject","name":"Whoza.ai for Landscapers — AI Call Answering Demo","description":"Watch Katie capture a missed landscaping enquiry in under 60 seconds. Garden design project answered instantly, details sent to WhatsApp, site visit booked while the landscaper is still on another job.","thumbnailUrl":["https://whoza.ai/og-image.png","https://whoza.ai/og-image-1200x630.png"],"uploadDate":"2026-05-06T00:00:00+00:00","duration":"PT60S","contentUrl":"https://whoza.ai/whoza-explainer.mp4","embedUrl":"https://whoza.ai/for-landscapers","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Whoza.ai","url":"https://whoza.ai","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://whoza.ai/logo.png","width":512,"height":512}},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Whoza.ai","url":"https://whoza.ai"},"potentialAction":{"@type":"WatchAction","target":{"@type":"EntryPoint","urlTemplate":"https://whoza.ai/for-landscapers","actionPlatform":["http://schema.org/DesktopWebPlatform","http://schema.org/MobileWebPlatform"]},"expectsAcceptanceOf":{"@type":"Offer","price":"0","priceCurrency":"GBP","availability":"https://schema.org/InStock"}}}15:Td94,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How much does AI call answering cost for landscapers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"whoza.ai starts at £59/month for the Starter plan. That's less than one small garden maintenance job. You get unlimited AI call answering, WhatsApp delivery, and a 7-day free trial with no credit card required. Most landscapers recover the cost within a week by capturing just one missed enquiry."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can Katie handle commercial landscaping enquiries?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Absolutely. Katie is trained to identify commercial enquiries from estates, hotels, property developers, councils, schools, and office complexes. She captures contract details, site addresses, project scope, and budget ranges — then marks these as priority in your WhatsApp alert. Commercial clients are your biggest repeat customer base, so Katie makes sure you never miss them."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What information does Katie collect from landscaping customers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Katie captures: full name, phone number, postcode, project type (garden design, maintenance, patio, decking, fencing, turfing, tree surgery, etc.), garden size, budget range, timeline, property type (residential/commercial), design vs maintenance preference, and how they found you. For emergencies, she also asks about storm damage extent and urgency level."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Will customers know they're talking to AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Katie introduces herself as your digital assistant with a natural, professional voice. Most callers appreciate the instant response over voicemail or a ringing phone. In user surveys, 89% of callers are satisfied with the AI experience — they just want their garden project started fast."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does it work with my existing business phone number?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. You simply set up call forwarding from your existing landscaping business number to your whoza.ai number. Your customers dial the same number they've always used — Katie just answers when you can't. Setup takes under 10 minutes."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How quickly can I get set up?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Most landscapers are live and capturing calls within 30 minutes. Sign up, connect your number via call forwarding, set your greeting and business details, and Katie starts answering immediately. No hardware, no IT team, no technical knowledge required."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can Katie handle emergency storm damage calls?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Katie answers 24/7 including nights, weekends, and bank holidays. She identifies emergency keywords like 'storm damage', 'fallen tree', 'flooding', and 'dangerous branches' — then marks the enquiry as emergency priority in your WhatsApp alert. You see it immediately and can respond within minutes."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What happens if Katie can't handle a complex enquiry?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Katie is trained to recognise when a call needs human attention. For complex garden design consultations or unusual projects, she takes a detailed message and flags it for your immediate callback. You receive the full context in WhatsApp so you can call back prepared with all the details."}}]}7:["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$12"}}],["$","$L13",null,{}],["$","$L14",null,{"items":[{"name":"Home","item":"https://whoza.ai"},{"name":"For Landscapers","item":"https://whoza.ai/for-landscapers"}]}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$15"}}],"$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b"],null,"$L1c"]}]
